><!--v-if--></button></div></div><!----></div></div></div></div><div data-v-73dff58c=""><div class="newsfeed-post" data-v-3a58b531="" data-v-73dff58c=""><svg class="co-icon newsfeed-post-delete" aria-hidden="true" ariadescribedby="co-popper-489" data-v-8ef67890="" data-v-3a58b531=""><use xlink:href="#co-icon-trash" data-v-8ef67890=""></use></svg><div data-v-3a58b531=""><a class="newsfeed-post-avatar" href="#team/746" data-v-3a58b531=""><div class="wa-letter-avatar" alt="" data-v-7fbcbe67="" data-v-3a58b531="" style="width: 44px; height: 44px; background-image: url(&quot;https://ca697e16014645.uk.deputy.com/assets/php/image_preview.php/746/135/135&quot;);"><!----></div></a><div class="newsfeed-post-author" data-v-3a58b531=""><a class="newsfeed-post-author-name" href="#team/746" data-v-3a58b531="">PAUL RAMPTON</a><div class="newsfeed-post-sub-text" data-v-3a58b531="">Mar 26, 2023 7:42 PM · <span class="wa-link" data-v-55dda85c="" data-v-3a58b531="">Terminal 5, Terminal 4 and 14 more</span></div></div><div class="newsfeed-post-content" data-v-3a58b531="">Language in the Workplace<br>
<br>
We have received some feedback regarding the different languages spoken in the workplace and how this is impacting staff morale.<br>
Our roles are often customer facing and require clear communication to prevent misunderstanding in relation to health and safety.<br>
Whilst we are mindful and supportive that our employees often come from a broad range of backgrounds and may have different customs and values, we remind all team members to consider the needs of others who may be present when using a language they don't understand.<br>
It is important that all members of our team are informed and feel included.<br>
