Please also make sure as you all know we have many new starters within company working on different locations, its everyone responsibility to explain/brief and pass relevant information’s regarding work task and locations. Please feel free to contact T/L, M/L, D/M for any additional information’s. All TL's please make sure that all new starters have signed onto the RAMS.<br>
